{"tid":942924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★12月16日 幣少爺預告下午派飯　但飯店唔知情","createTime":"2018-12-16T07:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T07:44:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3896ef6c4ea7e7a161b49d2ed214742bd0cc6430","tid":942924,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216125901842-1216_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181216145344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216125901842-1216_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181216145344&h=47a01fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗昨日(15日)天降鈔票事件，疑為搞手的幣少爺黃鉦傑在其fb貼文，指於今日(16日)準時下午4點直播，會在深水埗明哥的飯店做慈善，買飯票派比老人家。今早東網記者到明哥的飯店了解，但明哥要出席活動而不在店內，但職員均表示無人知道有關事件，他們一切工作如常。協助派飯的義工傅先生表示無收到通知，而他們本身今日亦有派飯活動，仍然如常進行。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方就此事件亦曾向明哥了解，但明哥本身什麼也不知道，亦未有收到任何人士通知有關事件，而飯店運作一切如常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181216/bkn-20181216125901842-1216_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181216%2Fbkn-20181216125901842-1216_00822_001.html&d=2DedmL28IKyHTBDmuYRUIJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=506eb917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181216/bkn-20181216125901842-1216_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cd6fd63aacffda1f9b5d6aeef357986ae570e511","tid":942924,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2aba68c09d36a924fad2ec54350e162c763c5c2","tid":942924,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12